{
  "stem": "3638.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I, I wasn't there daytime, so I did not experience all this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But each time we came at night, we had this happen, that happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody was killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somebody was hanged.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and you hear all the time the same thing, all the atrocities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, we did-- it was not very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're lucky that we came alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're lucky that we come out alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was-- that's where Schindler probably made a, made a, a-- what you call it-- commitment to build, to build this place on the-- At the factory.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the factory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, at the same thing-- because Bankier was coming with us, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't know what could happen to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In factory.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to my memory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is that what happened?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not to my-- maybe when I was in Plaszow, but we were never in Plaszow-- I was never in Plaszow at daytime.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was always working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Daytime, I was always working at Emalia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was all the time in Emalia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never had any day off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it wasn't so bad, because we didn't work-- I didn't work so hard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't remember it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The only time which I remember the factory was maybe closed, and we were in Plaszow, at the time where he had to transfer all the machinery from Plaszow into Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, we were staying in the, in the Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're not doing very much over there, and, and that's what-- the Schindler List was born there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what was-- we knew that he come one day, and he will make a list and take his people to the Brunnlitz, the people to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
